tax return, irrespective of turnover or profit. Clientfilling provides income tax filing services with dedicated Tax Expert support. Upload your Form-16, sit back and relax. Our experts will file your income tax return and provide you the acknowledgement within 1 - 2 business days.<\\/p><p class=\\"text-justify\\" style=\\"margin-bottom: 1.85714em; line-height: 28px;\\"><span style=\\"background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\\"><font color=\\"#7b7b7b\\" face=\\"Open Sans\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px;\\">Assessee filing ITR 5 form under the fourth method must complete the acknowledgement in ITR-V. After preparing ITR-V, the assessee should print out two copies of Form ITR-V. One copy of ITR-V, duly signed by the <\\/span><span style=\\"font-size: 14px;\\">assesses<\\/span><span style=\\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px;\\">, has to be sent by ordinary post to Post Bag No. 1, Electronic City Office, Bengaluru\\u2013560100 (Karnataka). The other copy may be retained by the <\\/span><span style=\\"font-size: 14px;\\">assesses<\\/span><span style=\\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px;\\">&nbsp;for his record.<\\/span><\\/font><\\/span><br><\\/p><p class=\\"text-justify\\" style=\\"color: rgb(123, 123, 123); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 1.85714em; line-height: 28px; letter-spacing: 0px;\\"><br><\\/p><\\/div><\\/div><\\/div><\\/section>","description":"Tax","header":"","footer":"","keywords":"","eq_check":"0","status":"1","timestamp":"2018-08-20 00:43:16"}]', '2018-08-20 00:37:18'),
