x;\\"><font face=\\"Times New Roman\\" color=\\"#003163\\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; of the mode of payment\\u2013cash, cheque or credit\\u2013and is linked to the PAN of the deductor and deductee.<\\/font><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><font face=\\"Times New Roman\\" color=\\"#003163\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 18px;\\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <\\/span><span style=\\"font-size: 18px;\\">A deductor has to deposit the deducted TDS to the government and the details of the same have to be filed in the form of a TDS return. A TDS return has to be filed quarterly. Different types of <\\/span><\\/font><\\/p><p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><font face=\\"Times New Roman\\" color=\\"#003163\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 18px;\\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; TDS deductions have to be filed using different.TDS return forms.<\\/span><span style=\\"font-size: 18px;\\">Preparing TDS returns can be done easily using the<\\/span><span style=\\"font-size: 18px;\\">&nbsp;clear TDS software&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/font><\\/p><p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><font face=\\"Times New Roman\\" color=\\"#003163\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 18px;\\"><br><\\/span><\\/font><\\/p><p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><font color=\\"#003163\\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <font face=\\"Times New Roman\\" style=\\"\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\\"font-size: 18px;\\">A deductor has to deposit the deducted TDS to the government and the details of the same have to be filed in the form of a TDS return. A TDS return has to be filed quarterly. Different types of TDS <\\/span><\\/font><\\/font><\\/p><p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 18px;\\"><font face=\\"Times New Roman\\" style=\\"\\" color=\\"#003163\\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;deductions have to be filed using different TDS return forms.<\\/font><\\/span><font color=\\"#085294\\" face=\\"Times New Roman\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 18px;\\"><br><\\/span><\\/font><\\/p>","description":"tds","header":"","footer":"","keywords":"","eq_